===Format===
*'''''Villager Esports DOMIN8R Series''' : June 5th - 8th
** '''Group Stage''' : ''June 5th -6th
*** 24 Teams will compete against each other in a round robin format.
*** 6 matches per day.
*** 24 Teams will be divided into 3 Groups
*** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16}} will qualify for '''Grand Finals'''{{VerticalMargin}}
** '''Grand Finals ''' : ''June 7th - 8th
*** Top 16 from Group Stage compete here for 2 days.
*** 6 matches per day.
